g.text: EleanorRank3Convo6 begins.

g.title: j238938502
g.text: You know what the best thing about Höllvania was, back before the Scaldra took over?

g.title: j1800121675
g.text: The nightlife?

g.title: j4259135807
g.text: The underground fighting circuit?

g.title: j119810772
g.text: The shopping?

g.title: j1996720298
g.text: No idea.

g.title: j865101221
g.text: Not interested. [End.]

g.title: j3287775409
g.text: Oh Gods. Surgically beautiful people getting their immaculate faces off on untested drugs? No.

g.title: j1855005961
g.text: Look. I have nothing against watching a pair of sweaty blokes go at one another, hard. But no.

g.title: j4018142255
g.text: Good guess. You could get anything from a Bresslin handbag and glove combo to a human eyeball on ice. But no.

g.title: j1114303349
g.text: Well, of course you have no idea. You're a fresh-faced newcomer.

g.title: j1119715525
g.text: Boo.

g.title: j2095086954
g.text: The bath houses!

g.title: Chat ends.
g.text: Chat ends.

g.title: j1472748855
g.text: I don’t know if they have anything like that where you are. They’re these temples, I suppose you’d call them, usually with a Sol set of rooms and a Lua set. You can soak in a public or a private pool. Everything smells herbal and steamy and it’s SO GOOD for getting your head back on straight.

g.title: j2423316329
g.text: Höllvania’s always had this hugely important tradition of ritual cleanliness. I guess it goes all the way back to the hot springs the city was built on.

g.title: j1230429409
g.text: All that ‘purity’ crap Viktor comes out with? He’s singing an age-old tune. All the citizens know where he’s coming from.

g.title: j997913373
g.text: I used to love paying the extra Höllars to have a musclebound professional pound all the tension out of my muscles. You’d have loved it. I’m sure you would.

g.title: j2984616017
g.text: I’m not so sure.

g.title: j2351648404
g.text: Sounds like my kind of fun.

g.title: j2081318143
g.text: What happened to them?

g.title: j316814572
g.text: You'll strut about in a suit made from an Infested human body, but draw the line at massages?

g.title: j3752135191
g.text: I knew you were my kind of squadmate.

g.title: j3157540922
g.text: I’m sure you can guess. The Techrot wrecked so much. There was no way the bath houses could stay open after the outbreaks.

g.title: j2452244390
g.text: Weird.

g.title: j1154488799
g.text: I wish some of the others were a bit less uptight. Sadly, there was no way the bath houses could stay open after the outbreaks.

g.title: j2394952150
g.text: From what I’ve seen, some of them are basically spawning pools now. It breaks my heart, to tell you the truth. I remember finding thousand-year-old marble and mosaic floors carpeted over with creeping flesh.

g.title: j3399937752
g.text: Do you have anything like that in your time?

g.title: j2816432304
g.text: Sacred public bath houses? No, not really.

g.title: j1474002252
g.text: So what do people do to unwind?

g.title: j2959680506
g.text: There’s Rathuum.

g.title: j2664324547
g.text: Some people bet on the Index.

g.title: j931863655
g.text: Komi has been around a while.

g.title: j2607397709
g.text: Sounds like Amir making sound effect noises to himself...

g.title: j379126522
g.text: Stockbrokers?

g.title: j3143172954
g.text: Komi? Black and white counters? The wedding-war of Sol and Lua?

g.title: j4268125099
g.text: It's a Grineer thing. It's ritual arena combat broadcast to the entire System.

g.title: j310839368
g.text: ... sort of? It's like a combination of stock trading and four-a-side violence. I know that sounds weird.

g.title: j1022306468
g.text: Um.. yes? Wait, is that what Komi's meant to represent?

g.title: j1221569705
g.text: It's a massive deal to them. Deadly serious.

g.title: j2759183924
g.text: The Corpus go absolutely crazy for it.

g.title: j4072090758
g.text: We only know it as a board game!

g.title: j2334706120
g.text: Dad and Arthur used to watch the wrestling together every Saturday night.

g.title: j176791691
g.text: But they're your enemies, aren't they? Or is there some kind of truce when it comes to team sports?

g.title: j1753591666
g.text: The Orokin loved it. It's even in Duviri.

g.title: j623463305
g.text: +10 Chemistry

g.title: j1060007930
g.text: +10 Chemistry

g.title: j2544175017
g.text: I had no idea it was THAT old, though.

g.title: j1539005941
g.text: Slip him some Rathuum tapes if you get the chance. I think he'd love it.

g.title: j1789982433
g.text: What am I saying? Of course there is. That's just how people are.

g.title: j4050393530
g.text: Old? It's SACRED! But also fun. A wonderful combination.

g.title: j1234689653
g.text: Everything's about the same two essential principles, you know? Mind and body. Symbol and meaning. Sol and Lua.

g.title: j1305308508
g.text: +20 Chemistry

g.title: j2628536505
g.text: Arthur and I used to play Komi every year at Solstice. Why did we ever stop?
